| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3569 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0ea48a0b-e8a1-5134-9a89-9cc57d0dfde2"
